DESCRIPTION:Welcome to Pokémon GO: Forever Forward!\n\nIn Pokémon GO\, S
 easons are periods of time that feature new events\, Pokémon debuts\, and
  surprises that all follow a certain theme. As the Seasons change\, you ma
 y find different Pokémon appearing in your area and hatching from Eggs. M
 ake sure to explore during each in-game Season to collect and train as man
 y different Pokémon as you can! You’ll also enjoy special bonuses as yo
 u do.\n\nMore info: https://leekduck.com/events/season-23-forever-forward/
